social_posts.post_text: Hi friends 🥹❤️! This is a PSA🎤: I will be returning to LA for the wintertime!! This hasn’t been an easy decision but I’ve realized I need to spend some quality time with my family and prioritize my well being. That being said- I will be closing my books at @editbeautyco for the next few months and will be in salon taking clients until December 21st. Would love to take care of everyone before I leave and if not I will be back in the springtime. And to all my LA friends/clients I’ll be home with all my hair, makeup, brow kits. Can’t wait to see you all!🫶🏼💓
What a year, I loved you 2022 🤎✨
